name: Kashyyyk: Skyhook Platform
LocationDStext: May place a card stacked here in owner's Lost Pile to draw two cards from Reserve Deck.
LocationLStext: While a Trandoshan present and you have no Wookiees on Kashyyyk, you may not modify or cancel opponent's force drains here.  (Original concept by Tom Frafjord - Rosemount Championship 2008)
